{"tid":1404413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［好撚眼訓啊屌你］車輪戰撚狗","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T15:55:05.000Z","uid":180285,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"caca94f7da3558cb2075ef9cc927fdd568390ec1","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:23:42.000Z","msg":"夜晚多區（3區或以上）集結無裝街坊，係狗宿舍樓下行人路開音樂會（車輛在馬路上參與）。人聲合唱，車聲伴奏。<br />\n<br />\n狗隻集結時/後即散，其他區隨即開始開音樂會。<br />\n狗隻散去後觀察情況後再開始音樂會。<br />\n如此類推。<br />\n<br />\n搞兩三轉真係成晚唔撚洗訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d5d5048ad7efdda4540cacc63cb3edf0e78d71","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:25:22.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"215e4a0f1dc7be9515e0b82586f9ef593a4cd7d1","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:26:09.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"c1b6ab0b54760372f0dbf15818048b0c7a972213","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"dc3fb277a6696d32d324e58d5aeb353b1cdbcd72","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"d6790dbba1b43ff63bfa899fa1bb37220a8645ef","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:29:30.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"543b5967a32760589fb357381fff92795e527564","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:31:24.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"a1d65d79aeb2242b2a17f3b8eb2ec7f5046f18d5","tid":1404413,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:36:00.000Z","msg":"罷工 罷訓"},{"pid":"9e4497cb133e3e74773f1f5b42d3d3e7961d93b0","tid":1404413,"uid":